    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2019-12-19</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2022-06-06T15:24:12Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Foreign National Firearms Background Check Enhancement Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires a nonimmigrant alien to get Department of Justice (DOJ) approval before purchasing a firearm. Specifically, the party transferring the firearm to the alien must receive a copy of the DOJ waiver or confirm with the DOJ that such an alien falls within specified exceptions, such as the alien possessing a U.S. hunting license. Currently, a nonimmigrant alien may acquire a firearm if the alien qualifies for one of the specified exceptions without acquiring DOJ approval.</p> </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
